# NAME

schoolmesh\_posixaccount\_repairbasefolder - Repair the basefolder of a user

# SYNOPSIS

schoolmesh\_posixaccount\_repairbasefolder *username*

# DESCRIPTION

Use this script to fix the permissions and the extended attributes for the basefolder of a user.

# EXAMPLES

	schoolmesh_posixaccount_repairbasefolder john

